products_flowers.name: ACDC
products_flowers.description: ACDC is a CBD-dominant Marijuana strain made from a phenotype of cannatonic. This strain produces little to no intoxicating effects. Medical Marijuana patients choose ACDC to help treat various ailments like pain,anxiety, epilepsy and the negative effects of chemotherapy.

products_flowers.name: Wild Thai
products_flowers.description:
Winner strain, 3rd place Best Sativa of connoisseur Cup 2019.
Wild Thai wil lift your mood and leave you in euphoria. If you are looking for an old school strain that will leave you energetic and motivated this is the perfect strain for you

products_flowers.name: Blue Dream
products_flowers.description: Blue Dream is a Sativa dominant hybrid Marijuana strain made by crossing Blueberry with Haze. Blue Dream is 18% THC but has a low CBD percentage, making this potent strain a fan favorite of both novice and veteran cannabis consumers.

products_flowers.name: Captain Crunch
products_flowers.description: As you might expect from the name, Captain Crunch is an accessible strain in flavor and delivers powerful sensations of sweetness that can positively affect  your  mood, especially if you suffer from chronic pain,  stress, or eating disorders.

products_flowers.name: Galactic jack
products_flowers.description: Galactic jack is a soaring Sativa-dominant hybrid  that is out of this world. Galactic jack provides an aroma of sweet lemons mixed with flavors of skunks grapefruit and effects best described as uplifting and carefree.

products_flowers.name: Jet fuel Gelato
products_flowers.description: Jet Fuel Gelato is 22% THC, making this strain an ideal  choice for experienced cannabis consumers.  Medical Marijuana patients often choose Jet Fuel Gelato when dealing with symptoms associated with depression, stress ,and anxiety.  Bred by Compound Genetics.

products_flowers.name: Moby Dick
products_flowers.description: Moby Dick is 17% THC, making it a good choice for new and experienced cannabis consumers.  Medical Marijuana patients say they choose this strain to relieve symptoms associated with stress, depression, and anxiety.

products_edibles.name: Magic Crack Pie
products_edibles.description: Crunchy oven baked oatmeal cookie crust filled with goey caramel custard.

products_edibles.name: Potcorn: Crack Pie
products_edibles.description: The classic buttered popcorn just got a revamp! We've added 100mg per box of THC & CBD and topped it off with fresh cannabis herb and our Crack Pie crust. This sweet a savory duo will add some extra chill your you Netflix and chill.

products_edibles.description: Vegan, sugar-free dark chocolate coated coffee beans. Bag contains 10 beans, each bean contains 2.5mg each. Great for beginners as you can portion out your doses easier!

products_edibles.name: Gummies
products_edibles.description: Vegan gummies in a mix of flavors: passion fruit, grape, green apple and raspberry. Bag contains 3 gummies, with 8mg of THC and CBD each.

products_edibles.name: Chocolate Bombs
products_edibles.description: Vegan, sugar free dark chocolate. 3 bombs come in the bag, with each chocolate containing 10mg of THC and CBD.

products_edibles.description: Soft baked chocolate chip cookies. Each box has 4 cookies, containing 15mg of THC and CBD each. (Contains dairy.)

reviews.author: Kevin Webber
reviews.content: Bought the cloud chasing cookies says eat half for a beginner I ate 2 full cookies with no affect. Waste of money

reviews.author: Lindsay Fulks
reviews.content: Great place for edibles!! They also have quality flower and pre-rolls but their signature THC pot-corn and convenient gummies are really where it’s at. They also have cute smoking accessories, and an indoor garden you can chill and smoke in.

reviews.author: ศิรกาณต์ มังสุรีย์
Heidi John
reviews.content: What a great cannabis shop! The products are all named so well (we loved the Potcorn!) and the space and atmosphere were super chill. I was lucky enough to meet Meen while I was there over Halloween. She invited us to smoke out of a pumpkin she had sculpted. Such a great time, thank you so much! Can't wait to come back and visit again soon.

reviews.author: Songkran Phothipunya
reviews.content: Great vibs, Great recommended for your healing and enjoy with Phuket trips. 🤤

reviews.author: A No Grainer
reviews.content: Amazing selection of treats and in such stylish packaging. Love this place and can’t wait to go back!
